articles.title: 21 Behind-The-Scenes Facts About Taylor Swift's Eras Tour That'll Make You Appreciate It Even More - BuzzFeed
articles.description: The bodysuit Taylor Swift wears during the Midnights section of the Eras Tour includes 5,300 hand-embroidered crystals and beads, and was designed by Oscar de la Renta.
